---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Dynamics 365 &mdash; Forge T Labs"
  description="Dynamics 365 implementation and support from Forge T Labs."
  canonical=""
  ogType="website"
  active="Services"
>
<main id="top">
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="hero-glow"></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="crumb"><a href="/">Home</a> &nbsp;/&nbsp; <a href="/services">Services</a> &nbsp;/&nbsp; Dynamics 365</div>
    <h1><em>Dynamics 365</em> business applications.</h1>
    <p class="lede">Connect sales, service, operations and finance on one Microsoft data platform. We implement, customise and support Dynamics 365 &mdash; and integrate it with the rest of your Microsoft Cloud.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head reveal">
      <span class="mono">What we deliver</span>
      <h2>Business applications, <em>implemented properly</em>.</h2>
      <p>Dynamics 365 only pays off when it fits how your business actually works. We configure and extend it around your processes &mdash; and keep it improving after go-live.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-cap">
      <div class="cap">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3fc878" stroke-width="1.6"><rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7" rx="1.5"/><rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7" rx="1.5"/><rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7" rx="1.5"/><rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7" rx="1.5"/></svg></div>
        <h4>Sales &amp; Customer Service</h4>
        <p>Pipeline, case management, SLAs and a connected customer record.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cap">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3fc878" stroke-width="1.6"><rect x="3" y="4" width="6" height="6" rx="1"/><rect x="15" y="14" width="6" height="6" rx="1"/><path d="M9 7h6a3 3 0 0 1 3 3v4" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div>
        <h4>Field Service</h4>
        <p>Work orders, scheduling and a mobile experience for field teams.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cap">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3fc878" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M4 20V4M4 20h16M8 16l4-5 3 3 5-7" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div>
        <h4>Business Central</h4>
        <p>Finance, inventory and operations on Microsoft's cloud ERP.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cap">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3fc878" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M12 3v6m0 6v6M3 12h6m6 0h6" stroke-linecap="round"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg></div>
        <h4>Customer Insights</h4>
        <p>Unified customer data, segments and AI-guided journeys.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cap">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3fc878" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M9 3v6m6-6v6M6 9h12v3a6 6 0 0 1-12 0V9ZM12 18v3" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></div>
        <h4>Data migration &amp; integration</h4>
        <p>Legacy data moved cleanly; Dynamics connected to your other systems.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cap">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3fc878" stroke-width="1.6"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3.2"/><path d="M12 2v3m0 14v3M2 12h3m14 0h3M5 5l2 2m10 10l2 2M5 19l2-2M17 7l2-2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></div>
        <h4>Managed support</h4>
        <p>Ongoing administration, enhancement and user support.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="band">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head reveal" style="margin-bottom:44px">
      <span class="mono">Use cases</span>
      <h2>Where this <em>delivers</em>.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-split">
      <div class="svc-list reveal">
        <div class="row">
          <span class="n">01</span>
          <div><h4>Replacing disconnected CRMs</h4><p>Consolidate spreadsheets and aging CRM tools into one Dynamics 365 customer record.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <span class="n">02</span>
          <div><h4>Service operations at scale</h4><p>Stand up case management, SLAs and a knowledge base for a growing support team.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <span class="n">03</span>
          <div><h4>Field service modernisation</h4><p>Move work orders and scheduling off paper and onto a mobile-first system.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <span class="n">04</span>
          <div><h4>Finance &amp; operations on one platform</h4><p>Run finance, inventory and operations on Business Central instead of separate tools.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <span class="n">05</span>
          <div><h4>AI-assisted selling</h4><p>Add Copilot capabilities so sellers spend less time on admin and more with customers.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-aside reveal">
        <h4>Industry spotlight</h4>
        <p class="lead-sm">Dynamics 365 applies across every sector &mdash; here is where we see it land hardest.</p>
        <div class="uc">
          <div class="h">Real estate &amp; construction</div>
          <div class="d">Project, client and subcontractor data on one platform &mdash; the same foundation our Forge suite is built on.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="uc">
          <div class="h">Professional services</div>
          <div class="d">Connecting pipeline, projects and resourcing for project-based firms.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="uc">
          <div class="h">Manufacturing &amp; distribution</div>
          <div class="d">Business Central for operations, inventory and field service.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="padding-top:40px">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="cta-band reveal">
      <div class="glow"></div>
      <h2>Dynamics 365 business applications. &mdash; let's talk.</h2>
      <p>Tell us where you are today and what you are trying to reach. We will map a practical
        path on the Microsoft Cloud.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/contact">Start a project &rarr;</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/services">All services</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</main>
</BaseLayout>
